### Auth Service — REST Client
### Extensão: REST Client (VS Code) | HTTP Client (JetBrains)

@base = http://localhost:3001
@kong = http://localhost:8000

@email = teste@ticketify.com
@password = senha12345
@name = Rafael Teste

### Após login, cole os tokens abaixo:
@accessToken = SEU_ACCESS_TOKEN_AQUI
@refreshToken = SEU_REFRESH_TOKEN_AQUI


### ─── Registro ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{base}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "{{name}}",
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###

### ─── Login ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{base}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###

### ─── Meu perfil ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###

### ─── Atualizar perfil ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

PATCH {{base}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nome Atualizado"
}

###

### ─── Refresh token ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{base}}/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### ─── Logout ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{base}}/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

###

### ─── JWKS (chave pública RS256) ─────────────────────────────────────────────

GET {{base}}/auth/.well-known/jwks.json

###

### ─── Via Kong (porta 8000) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

POST {{kong}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###

GET {{kong}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

###
